` FSx for ONTAP Forensic Investigation — Step 4: File Entity History
` All operations on a specific file path across all users and IPs.
` Token: $path$ (file path, e.g., /share/finance/report.xlsx)

index=fsxn_audit path="$path$"
| sort - _time
| table _time, user, operation, client_ip, result, svm, volume
| rename _time AS "Timestamp", user AS "User", operation AS "Operation",
         client_ip AS "Client IP", result AS "Result", svm AS "SVM", volume AS "Volume"
